### Get all rewards
GET http://localhost:3000/api/rewards

###
###
### Get all todos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/todos

###

###
### Get random Reward
GET http://localhost:3000/api/rewards/random

###
### Delete a reward
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/rewards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 3
}
### Create a new todo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

[{
  "task": "Add Rewards",
  "category": "Quest",
  "userId": 1
}]
###
### Update a todo
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 28,
  "completed": false
}

### Delete a todo
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 28
}


